From cou.: 16 (ii) Secondary effect: increase of the temperature.
From Soup: 16 (ii) Secondary effect: increase of the temperature.
 ###### 
From cou.: 17 (iii) Tertiary effect: variations in climate (different effects on the climate in different regions of the world): higher temperature peaks (cooler and warmer) drought, storms.
