From cou.: 20 The ISO standards EN ISO 14040 and 140445 also refer to the analysis of the data quality as a mandatory part of the LCIA. Since it is part of the Life Cycle Interpretation as well, it is further explained in the next section.
From Soup: 20 The ISO standards EN ISO 14040 and 14044 5 also refer to the analysis of the data quality as a mandatory part of the LCIA. Since it is part of the Life Cycle Interpretation as well, it is further explained in the next section.
